---
layout: base.njk
title: false
bodyClass: home
summary: "Domus Communis Foundation — data sovereignty, sovereign AI, and values-based technology for the common good."
---
<section class="cine-hero">
  <div class="cine-hero-bg"><img src="/assets/events/may-24/pecorario-1.jpg" alt=""></div>
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-hero-inner">
    <p class="cine-eyebrow">A global, Catholic-inspired foundation</p>
    <h1>A common home for <em>human-centered</em> technology.</h1>
    <p class="cine-dek">We bring together technologists, scholars, Nobel laureates, and faith leaders to ensure AI and emerging technology serve human dignity, peace, and the common good.</p>
    <div class="cine-cta-row">
      <a class="cine-btn-solid" href="/about/">Explore our work</a>
      <a class="cine-btn-text" href="/writing/">Read our writing →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cine-scroll">Scroll<span></span></div>
</section>

<section class="cine-manifesto">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <p class="cine-eyebrow">Our belief</p>
    <p class="big">Technology should empower the human person — never <em>replace</em> them.</p>
  </div>
</section>

{% set latestEssay = null %}
{% if collections.essays.length %}{% set latestEssay = (collections.essays | reverse)[0] %}{% endif %}
{% if latestEssay %}
<section class="cine-scene">
  {% if latestEssay.data.hero %}<div class="cine-scene-bg"><img src="{{ latestEssay.data.hero }}" alt=""></div>{% endif %}
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-scene-inner cine-reveal">
    <p class="cine-eyebrow">Featured{% if latestEssay.data.category %} · {{ latestEssay.data.category }}{% endif %}</p>
    <h2>{{ latestEssay.data.title }}</h2>
    {% if latestEssay.data.summary %}<p>{{ latestEssay.data.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
    <a class="cine-btn-text" href="{{ latestEssay.url }}">Read the essay →</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="cine-band">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <div class="cine-band-head"><div><p class="cine-eyebrow">What we mean</p><h3>Key concepts</h3></div></div>
    <div class="cine-concepts">
      <div class="cine-concept">
        <h4>Data Sovereignty</h4>
        <p>Individuals and entities hold full rights over their data — access, control, sharing, and value. Ownership stays with the original data creators.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cine-concept">
        <h4>Sovereign AI</h4>
        <p>AI architected to act for its human user — aligned to their values, following their commands — so autonomy stays with the person, not a third-party agent.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cine-concept">
        <h4>Value-Based AI Programming</h4>
        <p>AI designed to carry human values at its core, woven into the system rather than added after the fact.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cine-band">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <div class="cine-band-head">
      <div><p class="cine-eyebrow">Our work</p><h3>Initiatives</h3></div>
      <a href="/initiatives/">See all →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="cine-band-lead">Eight programs advancing human-centered technology — across peacebuilding, education, research, regulation, and faith.</p>
    <ul class="cine-inits">
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Peace</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Technology</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Academia</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Education</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Mentorship</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Research</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Regulatory</a></li>
      <li><a href="/initiatives/">Theology &amp; Philosophy</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cine-band">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <div class="cine-band-head"><div><p class="cine-eyebrow">The table we set</p><h3>Who we convene</h3></div></div>
    <p class="cine-band-lead">DCF bridges the worlds that must shape technology together.</p>
    <ul class="cine-convene">
      <li>AI &amp; Technology Actors</li>
      <li>Academia</li>
      <li>Nobel Laureates</li>
      <li>Faith Leaders</li>
      <li>Civil Society</li>
      <li>Institutions &amp; Governments</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

{% if collections.essays.length %}
<section class="cine-strip-sec">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <div class="cine-band-head">
      <div><p class="cine-eyebrow">Insights</p><h3>Latest writing</h3></div>
      <a href="/writing/">All writing →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cine-strip cine-reveal">
  {% for essay in (collections.essays | reverse).slice(1, 5) %}
    <a class="cine-frame" href="{{ essay.url }}">
      <div class="pic">{% if essay.data.hero %}<img src="{{ essay.data.hero }}" alt="">{% endif %}</div>
      {% if essay.data.category %}<span class="k">{{ essay.data.category }}</span>{% endif %}
      <h4>{{ essay.data.title }}</h4>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% set upcoming = [] %}
{% set past = [] %}
{% for event in collections.events %}
  {% if event.data.date | isPast %}{% set past = (past.push(event), past) %}{% else %}{% set upcoming = (upcoming.push(event), upcoming) %}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% set featuredEvent = null %}
{% set featuredIsPast = false %}
{% if upcoming.length %}{% set featuredEvent = (upcoming | sort(false, false, "data.date"))[0] %}{% elif past.length %}{% set featuredEvent = (past | sort(true, false, "data.date"))[0] %}{% set featuredIsPast = true %}{% endif %}

{% if featuredEvent %}
<section class="cine-scene">
  <div class="cine-scene-bg"><img src="/assets/events/may-24/muller-1.jpg" alt=""></div>
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-scene-inner cine-reveal">
    <p class="cine-eyebrow">{% if featuredIsPast %}Recent event{% else %}Upcoming event{% endif %}</p>
    <h2>{{ featuredEvent.data.title }}</h2>
    {% if featuredIsPast and featuredEvent.data.summary %}<p>{{ featuredEvent.data.summary }}</p>{% elif featuredEvent.data.subtitle %}<p>{{ featuredEvent.data.subtitle }}</p>{% endif %}
    <a class="cine-btn-text" href="{{ featuredEvent.url }}">View the event →</a>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

{% if collections.posts.length %}
<section class="cine-news">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <div class="cine-news-row">
      <h3>Newsroom</h3>
      <div>
      {% for post in (collections.posts | reverse).slice(0, 3) %}
        <a class="cine-ni" href="{{ post.url }}">
          <p class="date">{% if post.data.date %}<time datetime="{{ post.data.date | isoDate }}">{{ post.data.date | dateDisplay }}</time>{% endif %}</p>
          <h4>{{ post.data.title or post.data.summary or "Read post →" }}</h4>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% endif %}

<section class="cine-cta">
  <div class="cine-wrap cine-reveal">
    <p class="cine-eyebrow">Join the movement</p>
    <h2>Help ensure technology serves humanity.</h2>
    <a class="cine-btn-solid" href="/about/">Explore our work</a>
  </div>
</section>
